        "content": "<div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:100%; padding:6px 4px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:24px; font-weight:800; color:#f3f6fb; letter-spacing:0.01em; margin-bottom:4px;\">iDT4GDC</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.16em; color:#8aa1c7; margin-bottom:14px;\">Demo Navigation</div>\n  <a href=\"/d/idt4-connect/connect-data-centre?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">Connect Data Centre</a><a href=\"/d/idt4-overview/idt4gdc-overview?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">Overview</a><a href=\"/d/idt4-analytics/idt4gdc-analytics?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">Analytics</a><a href=\"/d/idt4-carbon/idt4gdc-carbon?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">Carbon</a><a href=\"/d/idt4-sustainability-kpis/sustainability-kpis?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">Sustainability KPIs</a><a href=\"/d/idt4-ai-optimisation/ai-optimisation?refresh=10s&${data_centre:queryparam}&${site_location:queryparam}&${site_ip:queryparam}&${username:queryparam}\" style=\"display:block; padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#111827; color:#d7dee9; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;\">AI Optimisation</a><div style=\"padding:10px 12px; margin:6px 0; border-radius:10px; background:#1f2937; color:#ffffff; font-weight:700;\">GPU\u2013FPGA Acceleration</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:auto; padding-top:16px; color:#93a1b5; font-size:12px; line-height:1.5;\">\n    Use the top selectors to set the active site and the Grafana time picker to change the analysis window.\n  </div>\n</div>",
